Blockchain & Cryptocurrency Beginner Course is a free, scholarship-based educational program offered by the Blockchain and Web3 Community Network (BWCN). Designed for absolute beginners, the course introduces participants to the fundamentals of blockchain technology, cryptocurrencies, and the broader Web3 ecosystem in an accessible and engaging format.

Offered at no cost as part of BWCN’s mission to promote inclusive tech education, the course empowers individuals—especially youth, women, and underserved communities—with the foundational knowledge and tools to confidently explore and participate in the world of decentralized technologies.

Participants engage in interactive sessions, hands-on wallet creation, real-world use cases, and open discussions, all within a supportive learning environment. Whether you're just curious or looking to enter the digital economy, this course offers a valuable and welcoming first step—completely free of charge.
